{"id": 728, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你遇到过哪些很萌的骗子，让你听完就笑了？", "description": "骗子是一个很容易产生谜样萌感的群体。", "record_count": 12985, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183505WmD0RPjxNq5ekSpH.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-31T11:07:33Z", "options": [{"id": 38918, "content": "我喜欢你啊.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236271}, {"id": 39697, "content": "开口就喊我妈，但那时我刚上大学。。。哪来的声音听起来比我还老的儿子，我也是醉了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347300}, {"id": 39698, "content": "扫一扫有惊喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347300}, {"id": 39705, "content": "里好，偶素东北滴黑涩会，你滴儿纸在我们的手上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410798}, {"id": 41243, "content": "完美无缺，一年没有骗子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422808}, {"id": 39708, "content": "a:这么冷的天你还穿丝袜不冷吗？ b:不冷！我穿裤子的话会长冻疮！       a:…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 41245, "content": "喂你快递到了\n哦！是吗？我不能下去，警察在抓我，我订了定时炸弹，我一按警察会和我同归于尽的，你快点!\n嘟嘟嘟嘟……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422808}, {"id": 45597, "content": "周一鹏最帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448474}, {"id": 39710, "content": "妈……我是你鹅几啊！（北方人笑过）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410844}, {"id": 39462, "content": "好好学！绝对前十名?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406743}, {"id": 60711, "content": "我是蒋介石的儿子......我特么还是李世民的女儿呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 38957, "content": "你怎么吃不胖呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395230}, {"id": 39213, "content": "5好急，至紧要快！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406158}, {"id": 42287, "content": "先生你好，你…哈哈哈…不好意思，这是我第一次骗人…哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176217}, {"id": 38705, "content": "你愿意跟我一起建立一个网店吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188036}, {"id": 40499, "content": "Hello, this is Tom.大家好，我是汤姆！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5448}, {"id": 38708, "content": "老师:昨晚作业有写吗？\n“有”\n那我检查一下\n然后大家都方了", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402117}, {"id": 38710, "content": "我就在你的身后，只需要你的一个回头！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402140}, {"id": 38966, "content": "为什么显示不完呢？是我打开方式不对？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400599}, {"id": 40506, "content": "橘子 橘子 不甜不要钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417799}, {"id": 38976, "content": "我不打算复习了，裸考", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404372}, {"id": 39233, "content": "王小龙是大傻逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396395}, {"id": 38722, "content": "没有呀，我什么都不会", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402205}, {"id": 39237, "content": "高考好好考，美好的大学生活在向你招手。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406300}, {"id": 38470, "content": "我们在一起吧~", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 38471, "content": "小额贷款居多，哪个是骗人的，哪个不是，我也分不太清，反正一块全拒绝了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398004}, {"id": 38472, "content": "你真美~又瘦了~", "image": null, "praise_count": 384, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 38473, "content": "喂 猜猜我……猜你老母啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 242, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306089}, {"id": 38474, "content": "我是你叔叔，我没有这样的叔叔，诶你别挂电话啊我真的是你叔叔（哭腔）", "image": null, "praise_count": 129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400483}, {"id": 38475, "content": "我现在不想找对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 451, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241868}, {"id": 38476, "content": "我给你介绍个对象，可漂亮了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 212, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 38988, "content": "球场上总会听见“我们不会打”，然后就没有然后了", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004653KtNdavye0LrVZmMc.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019697}, {"id": 38477, "content": "手机停机了，帮忙充点话费呗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400006}, {"id": 38479, "content": "我是你领导，哪个领导你听不出来吗？这是我私人号码，明天到我办公室一趟…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1738, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400006}, {"id": 38480, "content": "两个长得还行的男生，拦住我说他们的钱包被偷了，跟我借钱打！！！车！！！明明手里拿着手机，居然还跟我说如果需！要！他们还的话会给我充话费，我只好说你们找警察吧，我帮不了你们", "image": null, "praise_count": 456, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258549}, {"id": 38736, "content": "你牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402404}, {"id": 38481, "content": "哈哈男男女女就斤斤计较斤斤计较斤斤计较斤斤计较家姐姐家红红火火斤斤计较斤斤计较斤斤计较家姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐姐家斤斤计较斤斤计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396891}, {"id": 38482, "content": "gvbbb", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193721LuYtBrceOfNwQxMJ.jpg", "praise_count": 585, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396891}, {"id": 38483, "content": "朋友QQ被盗让我帮在网上充话费，当时不确定，机智地回了不会", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120503}, {"id": 38486, "content": "你好，我是移动公司的，送你“山”个月流量", "image": null, "praise_count": 496, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 38744, "content": "喂，下午来下我办公室。\n你谁啊\n我谁，你不知道我是谁？\n此时老子已经知道是骗子了 就说 哦哦 赵老师吧\n哎 对了\n那个那个 赵老师 咱们师母那个梅毒好了没有？\n啊？ 你。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402588}, {"id": 38489, "content": "兄弟，你媳妇怀孕了你不知道？", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343791}, {"id": 38490, "content": "香港公证处最后通知！您的手机号已被我公司抽取为幸运号码！奖金500万blablablabla…！", "image": null, "praise_count": 393, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294200}, {"id": 39003, "content": "xxx同学，我是你的x老师，你又未领取的奖学金请到…（老子成绩一般何来的奖学金）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280157}, {"id": 38493, "content": "我配不上你", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323525}, {"id": 38494, "content": "一辈子只谈一次恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323525}, {"id": 38495, "content": "点击就送屠龙宝刀，哈哈哈哈哈，这么能耐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209295}, {"id": 39007, "content": "约旅游～一直被放鸽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222546}, {"id": 38496, "content": "喂～您好，我是交通银行卖保险的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400562}, {"id": 38497, "content": "地铁站碰到借钱的，我说我没零钱，人说“你误会了我不要零钱，你给我一百的就好”我去你大爷的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 647, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}]}